{"tid":826353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[智將] 楊潤雄:家長可決定明日是否讓子女上學","createTime":"2018-09-18T07:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T16:19:46.000Z","uid":77196,"like":124,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"f281542af8ad1c84cee299fef8c0cb00e81e4d80","tid":826353,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:51:25.000Z","msg":"教育局表示，經過兩日清理及維修校舍和設施後，一般已可供如常上課，故宣布全港學校明日復課。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄在facebook帖文，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呼籲家長切記安全第一，可因應實際的交通及安全情況，決定是否安排子女上學</strong></span>；而同學即使因交通問題而遲到，學校亦會寛鬆處理。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又稱，個別在超強颱風中較受影響的學校，可能需要多些時間處理校舍的問題，教育局會全力支援，請家長留意校方的通知。"},{"pid":"3c1e6c0306a22397ec9f858531278f3361e5b60d","tid":826353,"uid":58031,"like":407,"dislike":4,"score":403,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:56:57.000Z","msg":"家長決定返唔返學<br />\n學校決定記唔記過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93c56281d3827c88355e20393da0971ac3e0afb","tid":826353,"uid":29702,"like":203,"dislike":2,"score":201,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54594db45d9f2902971cf6a22071c8365f282330","tid":826353,"uid":77196,"like":33,"dislike":5,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"f93c56281d3827c88355e20393da0971ac3e0afb","tid":826353,"uid":29702,"like":203,"dislike":2,"score":201,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"你個名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec0c17479f6eea3894775af048d64d02c15cb07","tid":826353,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:00:19.000Z","msg":"唔返當曠課<br />\n你諗你"},{"pid":"33421b8f3e8558a49e2a26c4cf60413cc76bcced","tid":826353,"uid":158078,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"返唔返工交返比d公司決定<br />\n返唔返學交返比d家長決定"},{"pid":"677f73e6aa5d1f04bc54bb648144eb61c1b4bb99","tid":826353,"uid":177047,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"c